 Galvatron stopped he sensed her desire to meet  her old friends. This was a 
lost cause. And no one as of yet new he was alive. So he made the decesion to 
abandon this mission and went back to the ship on the way he saw a bug 
mountain. His frustraion and anger from all his life;s tortures boiled to the 
surface. He made a giant ball of energy from his hands and incenerated the 
mountian. A mushroom cloud hit the sky. It took out almost all his energy. He 
slowly glided towrds his home base.
